# reasoning-llama-ai

reasoning-llama-ai is a reasoning-focused local LLM chat application powered by:

- Quantized Llama 3
- llama.cpp
- FastAPI
- Docker
- Modern ChatGPT-style UI

It runs fully locally using GGUF models and provides an interactive web-based AI chat experience with markdown and LaTeX rendering support.

[docker image](https://hub.docker.com/r/mohdmusheer/reasoning-llama-ai)

---

# Features

- Quantized GGUF Llama 3 inference
- llama.cpp backend
- FastAPI API server
- Responsive modern UI
- Markdown rendering
- LaTeX math rendering
- Dockerized deployment
- CPU inference support
- Streaming-ready architecture

---

# Tech Stack

- Python 3.11
- FastAPI
- llama.cpp
- Docker
- JavaScript
- HTML/CSS
- Jinja2

